{"tid":1427022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［我撐警］警察遊樂會成警員臨時休息中心","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:06:35.000Z","uid":55115,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac651953ae773493f5f4689f5ce144f82d7948b","tid":1427022,"uid":55115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b1uw3nx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb1uw3nx.png&h=9c5f9b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//辛苦了！多謝你們保護我們的家園//<br />\n<br />\n【非常時期】警察遊樂會成警員臨時休息中心<br />\n<br />\n面對多星期突發衝突，警察疲於奔命到各區維持治安，太子警察遊樂會的籃球場，亦成警員臨時休息中心，方便隨時調派警員執勤。<br />\n<br />\n原圖：讀者提供<br />\n<br />\n網站連結：<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/港人花生/47289/-非常時期-警察遊樂會成警員臨時休息中心\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%8A%B1%E7%94%9F%2F47289%2F-%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%99%82%E6%9C%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%81%8A%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83%E6%88%90%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=c04627b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/港人花生/47289/-非常時期-警察遊樂會成警員臨時休息中心</a><br />\n<br />\n#警察遊樂會 #撐警 #支持警察<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察們辛苦了。我地愛國愛黨的連登仔要唔要撐下佢地，支持佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc94f15a71e412b135d3d30e7fde71301daf6c38","tid":1427022,"uid":55115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"推到有愛警人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe991dfee34cea2023c85cc16f72a6ed5ea1346","tid":1427022,"uid":133033,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"係門口聲援未呀"},{"pid":"00353c04e44a7dbc4c2e5bcd0825de41ab8df1cd","tid":1427022,"uid":261914,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:44:52.000Z","msg":"其實係咪驚到唔敢返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\"